             was indicted for <rs id="t17951028-24-off133" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17951028-24-off133" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17951028-24-off133" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17951028-24-cd134" type="crimeDate">3d of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17951028-24-off133 t17951028-24-cd134"></join>, a pewter quart pot, value 13d. a leather strap, value 2d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17951028-24-victim285" type="victimName">
                     Stephen 
                     Noad
                  <interp inst="t17951028-24-victim285" type="surname" value="Noad"></interp>
